                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for producing magnesium oxide and co-producing methanol through hydrogenation refining of magnesium carbonate",
                    "一种碳酸镁加氢炼制生产氧化镁及联产制甲醇的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a method for producing magnesium oxide and co-producing methanol by hydrogenation reduction refining of magnesium carbonate. The method comprises the following steps: (1) carrying out reduction refining on magnesium carbonate under the conditions of green hydrogen atmosphere and different roasting temperatures to produce magnesium oxide; and (2) converting carbon resources in carbonate into methane and carbon monoxide through reduction refining, and producing high value-added chemicals such as methanol and the like with excessive hydrogen under mild conditions. According to the method, emission reduction of carbon dioxide in the magnesium carbonate pyrolysis process can be realized, the decomposition temperature of magnesium carbonate is reduced, production energy consumption is reduced, novel'green 'magnesium oxide with a low carbon background is obtained, carbon resources in magnesium carbonate can be converted into high-added-value chemicals such as methanol, and the method has a wide application prospect."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种碳酸镁加氢还原炼制生产氧化镁及联产制甲醇的方法。该方法包括：(1)碳酸镁在“绿氢”气氛和不同焙烧温度条件下还原炼制生产氧化镁(2)将碳酸盐中的碳资源通过还原炼制转化成甲烷、一氧化碳并和过量的氢气在温和条件下生产甲醇等高附加值化学品。该方法既可以实现碳酸镁热解过程二氧化碳的减排，降低碳酸镁的分解温度，减少生产能耗，获得低碳背景的新型“绿色”氧化镁，又可以将碳酸镁中的碳资源转化为甲醇等高附加值化学品，具有广阔的应用前景。"
                }
            ]
